description: Spider-Man faces off against the unstoppable Juggernaut.
name: Nothing Can Stop the Juggernaut

volume.name: The Sensational Spider-Man - Nothing Can Stop the Juggernaut

description: The Authority's most outrageous tales are collected together in this third trade paperback. In the primary story of this edition, the Authority team must devise a way to fight the Earth after a renegade doctor bent on genocide puts a mad plan in action that has the planet itself rebelling against its inhabitants. Next, the team must fight against some former friends who have returned from the dead with a murderous agenda as well as tackle an insane ex-hero who is more powerful than all of them combined.
name: TPB

volume.name: The Authority: Earth Inferno and Other Stories

description: A treasure of 14 charming stories about family, friends, couples and unexpected bonds. Written by Natsume Ono over ten years, here is the long-awaited collection of her early work, including numerous illustrations and previously unpublished stories!
name: Vol. 1

description: Princess Nakaba of Senan and Prince Caesar of Belquat only married each other for the sake of peace between their two warring countries, but things take a surprising turn when Caesar finds himself falling for his strange wife! Caesar tries to get Nakaba to return his feelings, but she maintains that he is her enemy and that she hates him. So when Nakaba has a vision of Caesar getting killed, will she say anything to save him?
name: Vol. 2

description: The battle between Kohaku and Shuri has ended, but Sakura is still held captive by Enju. Sakura tries to convince her brother that there are humans who will accept the moon people, but he will not back down. Enju tells Sakura she will soon need to choose sides and whom she is to destroy...
name: Vol. 6

volume.name: Sakura Hime: The Legend of Princess Sakura

description: Secretly taking a baking class for men, Asuka is relieved that there's a safe haven where he doesn't need to hide his girly side from his anti-otomen mother. But when she finds out that he's been attending this class, things get set to explode!
name: Vol. 12

description: Natsume and Tanuma are spending a rainy day helping Taki clean up a storehouse full of her grandfather's stuff. But old clothes and books aren't the only things sealed away. The friends accidentally release a very angry yokai. Is teamwork enough to stop the yokai from going on a rampage?!
name: Vol. 11

description:
Hikaru's big brother is working for the enemy, and he wants to reunite with Hikaru. Meanwhile, someone is posting negative reviews on the library's website, and Kasahara intends to find out who. Later, personal issues are set aside when the Library Forces find out about a book burning on their home turf!

Chapters 29-33 & two bonus manga.
name: Vol. 7

description: Mizuki loves living at the shrine with Nanami, but he hates that he has to stay behind when she goes to school. He hates even more that Tomoe gets to go with her. But Mizuki isn't used to the human world, so Nanami thinks it's safer if he just stays put. Can Mizuki become a master of the mundane, or will his secret foray into town end in disaster?!
name: Vol. 7

description: The Eight Guardians have lost their memories of each other and Akane, shattering the mystical bond between them. Akane's only hope is to find the Curse Seed, which has the power to restore their memories. But can she fight the Demon Clan, protect the Capital and break the curse without the Guardians by her side?
name: Vol. 15

description: There's a dark legend in Bordeaux's underworld, about the powerful gangster, Brungevin. Allegedly, he never peels his gloves off, because a simple touch of his hands can be deadly. But who's Brungevin, in truth? Just a miserable pimp who exploits prostitutes, or the reincarnation of a slaver from 300 years before? Harlan Draka and friends will have to find the the awful truth about him...
name: Il divoratore di anime

description: Milo and the rest of the gobs have finished turning the hollowed-out body of a dead giant into a pub. They reward themselves with a fun, refreshing dip in the old swimming hole. Yay! Splishy-splashy fun! ...Oh, and the giant comes to life and goes on a deadly rampage.

Norway. A room with a curse on it, number 13, in an old hotel in Alesund. A fresco of the Last Judgment discovered under a layer of plaster in an ancient church. An inscription in Latin that is best not recited aloud. Two sinister cloaked figures persecuting a young woman whos working as an art restorer. A missing professor What does all this have to do with the diabolical Count Magnus Oland, whos the sworn enemy of Queen Christina of Sweden and has been dead for centuries?
name: Il conte Magnus

description: The gang's new pubbuilt in the petrified body of a dead giantis now less a quaint drinking spot, more a reanimated killing machine rampaging through the countryside. Houses are smashed, elves are eaten...and the Gobs finally decide they may have to leave their afternoon at the swimming hole and get involved.

The thrilling conclusion to the story no one demanded is almost here. So many questions, so few of them matter: Will the gang be able to stop the runaway, reanimated giant before it kills hundreds and racks up some serious fines? Will Gretch' find the courage to tell Milo how she really feels? Can Heather be dressed down any further without becoming truly blatant? Check out #4 and see...

While spending a romantic evening with Sarah, Nathan comes across a young thief. The meeting shakes him: the girl, Lara, seems to know him fairly well, although he does not have no memory of her. The young, moreover, is not able to provide more details, forcing Nathan to take a difficult personal investigation: with the help of Darver and Elania Elmore, head of the Security Council, the Alfa agent goes back to a dangerous mission of some years before, a story that hides a terrible secret.
name: Memorie rubate

description: George Celebrate the 40th Anniversary of a true iconic horror movie classic! Night of the Living Dead co-creator John Russo brings you a new tale of terror set during the night that changed the world forever. The eastern United States is in chaos as hordes of the undead wage war against the living, and increasingly frantic television transmissions are the only source of information available to a terrified populace. But there is no escape from the living dead and no safe place to hide, not even the WIIC-TV studio where original Night of the Living Dead news anchorman Chuck Blaine has some difficult decisions to make: Should his heroic news crew continue their emergency public broadcasts, or run from the army of ghouls amassing outside the station? More importantly, should he continue to disseminate questionable government recommendations that could be luring viewers into inescapable death traps? This special bonus-sized tale features appearances by some of the original film's most memorable characters, including the recently deceased Johnny, Barbra, and little Karen Cooper! This jumbo size issue is available with Regular, Gore, Rotting, and Terror covers by interior artist Edison George, and a Painted cover by Lucio Rubira. As special treat, there is a Triple Cast Signed Edition that is signed by original actors John Russo, Russ ('Johnny') Streiner and the very rare autograph of George ('Sheriff') Kosana, that comes packaged with a Certificate of Authenticity and is limited to just 350 copies.
name: Annual 1

volume.name: Night of the Living Dead Annual

description: It's Valentine's Day in Richville! What will Richie get Gloria this year? Will Reggie get any Valentine's cards? And just what is Mayda Munny up to now? We lead off with an all-new 'classic-style' story by Richie Rich co-creator Sid Jacobson with art by Ernie Colon! And we follow that up with classic reprints of gift-giving fun that have all been digitally re-mastered and re-colored! It's enough to make you feel like a million bucks!
name: 2012 Valentines Special

description: Luther Jackson was a mutant: with extraordinary powers, he decided to put at the service of law and order his incredible skills, fighting crime, becoming a superhero: Eagleman. Today, Luther is a man destroyed by a terrible disease, the PDS or Progressive Debilitating Syndrome, confined to a wheelchair, reduced to a shadow of himself. Luther knows that the disease does not give him hope. He knows the end is near. But he became convinced that the end could have been put off if they had not come into play dirty interests of Big Pharma ... An opponent maybe too powerful for Nathan Never and Alfa Agency .
name: Affari sporchi

description: Plymouth, a town in the heart of the country, once thriving and now demoted to the rank of "ghost town". Yet, in that apparent calm in those abandoned buildings, tunnels and sewerage in the streets, something hovers in the shadows: monsters on the prowl to appease their hunger . Nathan, arrived by accident during a simple routine mission, along with a pair of misfits tries to bring home the skin and finds that the strange graffiti scrawled on the walls seem to be able to keep out those beings
name: Terrore senza nome

description:
Introducing one of the strip's most beloved characters, the mysterious Punjab the Wizard, and including one of the most famous Little Orphan Annie stories of all-that of the brilliant Eli Eon, who invents a material that never wears out and promises to make the world a better place for everyone.

Unfortunately, for both Eli and the world, evil forces are determined to steal his formula and use it for their own purposes. The only ones in their way are Annie, 'Daddy' Warbucks, and their new ally, the indomitable Punjab! Includes all dailies and color Sundays from February 1, 1935 through September 30, 1936.
name: Volume Six: Punjab the Wizard

volume.name: Little Orphan Annie: Never Say Die!

name: The Brothers of Justice ; Waliangoolu Traitor

volume.name: Edgar Rice Burroughs Tarzan of the Apes

description: Reprints the last two issues of Edlund's original Tick series; 11 and 12. Also includes 20 pages of unpublished Edlund Tick art plus a sneak preview peak at The Tick 13!

volume.name: The Best of Captain Marvel Rides the Engine of Doom!
Jim Henson's Muppets Short, Green and Handsome

description:
UNTITLED by Angie Wang

COLLEGE GIRL BY NIGHT by Michael DeForge

DIRTY DEEDS by Brandon Graham

SLIME WORM by Mickey Zacchilli

EARLY BIRD by Lisa Hanawalt

A color strip by True Chubbo

A pinup poster by Jillian Tamaki
name: Thickness

description:
BREEDING SEASON by Katie Skelly

GRANDADDY PURPLE, EROTIC GAMESHOW by Jonny Negron

PEARL DIVERS by Ze Jian Shen

TRAP SHADEZ by Derek Ballard

A color strip by True Chubbo
name: Thickness

description: A collection of ilustrations of The Batman Chronicles' heroes and villains by different artists.
name: The Batman Chronicles Gallery

description: Deadly beetles swarm over the land, killing crops and people alike. But are they what they seem? Behind the deadly attacks hides an enemy that even Zein may not beat.
name: Enter the Scarab

description:
1. Character Designs

2. Mechaphysical

3. Construct - Part One of Six

Who sank Atlantis? Mera, the beautiful Atlantean assassin trained in the Bermuda Triangle, follows a trail of death and deceit to the one man who knows the ugly truth. But what does he want in return for his secrets and how does it all tie into Mera's own dark past?
name: Deserted!

description: Batman's darkest fears resurface in this stunning conclusion to the opening epic as the Dark Knight confronts the mastermind behind the toxin being injected into Gotham City's criminals. But the conspiracy behind the toxin runs deeper than he could possibly have imagined. Time is running out and the entire structure of Gotham City's society is at risk, unless Batman can find a path to overcome the man who once broke his back: Bane!
name: Run Rabbit Run

description: While the rest of the field team puts down a sudden uprising of rogue technology, Irish and Attila make the most of their medical leave by getting wasted in an Eastern European dive bar though the locals don't take kindly to having U.N. peacekeepers nosing around in their business
name: Obsolescence, Part 1: Technical

description: Struggling with the climactic aftermath of his battle with Mob Rule last issue, The Flash must solve a murder mystery that dates back 150 years! Is this case too cold even for Barry Allen? Also: Learn the origins of Central and Keystone City!
name: Best Served Cold

description: In the blink of an eye, Ronnie and Jason witness a horror so gruesome, the two young Firestorms will question their entire futures as Super Heroes. As if that wasn't enough, Pozhar, the Russian Firestorm, shows the two boys exactly how dangerous their world has become.
name: An Aftermath of Rage

volume.name: The Fury of Firestorm: The Nuclear Man

description: The sleeper in the sun has awakened! Green Lantern Kyle Rayner and his renegade team of Lanterns are all that stands between the creature Invictus and planetary genocide. But in this battle, how did Fatality and the rest of the Lanterns end up being the bad guys?
name: Rage of Angels

description: It's a shock ending you won't see coming! Guest star Batman grudgingly helps Andrew fight the Queen of Blood, who has taken over Gotham City with her army of vampires! But Mary's going to lose something dear to her in the process! Come see why the Internet is raving about this great new series that mixes Super Heroes and horror!
name: This Charming Man
